091EA8DD.Line13.6D03F: (grunt) There may have also been a brawl with a goat over this...patch of mud. I like to think I triumphed.

5A1F4B4A.Line1.6D03F: (groan) Bloody damn hells. What do you want?

5B6C043C.Line21.6D03F: (wince) I thought I did once. His name is Elias. He was my apprentice.

69E26198.Line15.BAE4: Lorath, who is the Pale Man?

7337041C.Line19.BAE4: Horadrim?! Then you must know him.
